latestIgtvVideos.title: #technotogether
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
First time i heard techno was in awakenings in ade last year it was @realadambeyer set and @carlcoxofficial  set. Since then i started loving this genre so much that i dug deep into it and explored a new world all together. Even tho i play and produce tech house music, which is anyways a hybrid from techno. I dont know what attracted me and how it attracted me so much. 

In these tough times its very important for all the techno lovers and artists to come together and Unite for our common feeling as its more than just music

Really looking forward to play a tech house to techno set in my community venture @vv.ravecommunity launch party BLACKLISTED Super excited 😍🙌🏼
.
.
#technovibes #techhouselover #techno #technomusic #technolife #technolovers

latestIgtvVideos.title: Afrojack heard my demos and liked them😍🙌🏼
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Afrojack is one of those artist whom i listened to a lot in my initial days of dance music discovery. Till today some of his iconic tracks are in my playlist. I submitted my tracks to his live stream and so happy that he heard almost all of them😍, more happy by the fact that he liked them and gave me a good constructive feedback🙌🏼 Thanks a lot @afrojack for being an inspiration to lot of upcoming producers out there like me.

.
.
.
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: @chrislake heard my demos and he liked them😍😍🙌🏼.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Super Happy😍😍😍😍 by such an positive response from @chrislake on 4 of my demos. Finally after a month waiting for my demos to appear on @blackbookrecords demo submission twitch stream. Staying away for the night due to time zone difference this was the best moment for me this year. Chris even said that hes looking forward to listen to more stuff from me. M literally feeling like m top of the world right now

Thanks a lot @chrislake for such a positive as well as a constructive feedback to improve. You have been the biggest influence for all my house music productions so far. Hope so you would love my upcoming stuff, ill send you more🙌🏼🙌🏼🙌🏼

#chrislake #twitch #techhouse #housemusic #housemusiclover #blackbookrecords #feedback #housemusicallnightlong #ravefamily #rave #plur #kratexmusic
